hat pop out up to six mini spiders at a time.  the spiders are blue to me at 62, don't hit particularly hard, and are very easy to AE mez.  problem with em is they will camp your monk, and are totally unsplittable.  The highlight of the camp (other than the named) are the two fiendish consorts.  They are lvl 63, hit for a max of 668 (that I've seen), and have approximately 1/3 drop rate of parchments (50/50 etherial/spectral).  They are on a one hour spawn time, so in a four hour exp run its not uncommon to see 4 or 5 drop.  Hope this helps at all, and good luck on the earring.<br>
<br>
Grendon Ralf, 62 Ogre Warlord of Rallos-Zek<br>
